# [Command] _nginx deployment configuration analyze_

Analyze an NGINX configuration without applying it to the NGINXaaS deployment

#### examples

- Config package dry run
    ```bash
        nginx deployment configuration analyze --deployment-name myDeployment --resource-group myResourceGroup --configuration-name default --config root-file=<nginx.conf> package='{data:}'
    ```
